activate.ChoosePassPhraseSeeSuggestions: Khetha ibinzana elidlula ukuvikela i-akhawunti yakho. Bona ukusikisela kwemibono ethile.
activate.IfYouFeel: Uma uzizwa ukuthi kukhona okungahambi kahle, ungakwazi

notifications.title: Imvume
notifications.prompt: Ingabe ufuna ukunika amandla izaziso? Uzothola izibuyekezo zangempela-isikhathi mayelana nezinto ozikhathalelayo.
notifications.WelcomePleaseVerifyEmail: Siyakwamukela! Sicela uqinisekise ikheli lakho le-imeyili.
notifications.CompletedActivationLogIn: Uqede ukwenza kusebenze umsebenzisi. Zama ukungena ngemvume manje.

login.title: Uyemukelwa
login.resendConfirm: Ngabe ufuna ukuthumela umlayezo ukuze usethe kabusha umushwana wakho wokungena?
login.resendSuccess: Bheka umyalezo ukuze usethe kabusha umushwana wakho wokungena
login.noPassphrase: Ngaphambi kokuthi ungene ngemvume, kufanele usethe ibinzana lokudlula ngokuchofoza isixhumanisi kumyalezo wakho wokuqalisa.
login.notVerified: Kufanele uzithumele umyalezo wokwenza kusebenze ukuze ungene ngemvume.
login.emailExists: Wake wazama ukubhalisa nalesi imeyili ngaphambili? Uma kunjalo, hlola ibhokisi lakho lokungenayo ukuze usebenzise i-akhawunti yakho. Chofoza ukuze uthumele futhi umyalezo
login.mobileExists: Wake wazama ukubhalisa nale nombolo yeselula ngaphambili? Uma kunjalo, hlola i-SMS yakho ukuze usebenzise i-akhawunti yakho. Chofoza ukuze uthumele futhi umyalezo
login.facebookNoEmail: I-akhawunti yakho ye-facebook ishoda ngekheli le-imeyili eliqinisekisiwe. Mane ungene ngemvume ngendlela yendabuko.

alert.title: Iqondisa kabusha ku-Wallet
alert.content: Lapho usuvale le ngxoxo, uzoyiswa esikhwameni sakho semali. Ngemuva kokungena ngemvume, buyela kuleli khasi.

facebook.noEmail: I-akhawunti yakho ye-facebook ishoda ngekheli le-imeyili eliqinisekisiwe. Vele ungene ngendlela yomdabu.
